body.codeblock:
/* Hide sections below level 3. */
*[class ~= "map/topicref"][is-chapter] >
    *[class ~= "map/topicref"]:not([is-chapter]) >
    *[class ~= "map/topicref"] >
    *[class ~= "map/topicref"] {
    display: none;
}

body.p:
 If you want to increase the TOC depth, so that topic references on level 3 or higher could be visible, you should overwrite this rule in your customization CSS,
            like:*[class ~= "map/topicref"][is-chapter] >
    *[class ~= "map/topicref"]:not([is-chapter]) >
    *[class ~= "map/topicref"] >
    *[class ~= "map/topicref"]{
    display:block;
}
